data.title: US EPA approved Monsanto's new Genetic-Engineering Technology
data.content: US EPA approved the use of DvSnf7 dsRNA, an RNA interference (RNAi) based insecticide technology. Monsanto expects corn seed with RNAi to be on the market by the end of this decade.
